Information.LongDescription: Overlooking Baltimore's beautiful Inner Harbor and ideally located within walking distance of Little Italy and Fells Point, Spinnaker Bay is the centerpiece of the new Harbor East. Professionally managed by Bozzuto, this prestigious residence features 315 premium apartment homes designed and appointed with the tremendous care for which Bozzuto is known across the region. At Spinnaker Bay, we've taken the time to perfect the balance of waterside tranquility and city excitement. There's a reason Harbor East has become Baltimore's most sought-after neighborhood. Featuring incredible new stores and restaurants, and just a short walk to Fells Point, the Inner Harbor and Downtown, Harbor East is the city's new urban center. Convenient to work and play, Spinnaker Bay offers the best location. Harbor East offers exciting shopping and sparkling water views that combine to create one of Baltimore's most beautiful places to live. Stroll around the harbor and explore the vibrant streets.

Pet.Comment: Breed restrictions apply. Dogs over 35 lbs: $75/month rent, $500 refundable pet deposit.

Information.LongDescription: The Promenade at Inner Harbor East, a harborside community in the heart of the city. Imagine living where you could enjoy all the excitement and culture of the city life, along with the quiet charm of a harborside community. That's the lifestyle you'll enjoy at The Promenade, Baltimore's most prestigious waterfront address at Inner Harbor East. Envision the dramatic city skylines and sweeping water vistas you'll proudly share with guests. Enjoy the exciting new Harbor East retails and dining. Walk to the Inner Harbor and downtown business district. Inside The Promenade you'll find all luxurious amenities and conveniences to suit your lifestyle including newly renovated common areas and apartments. We feature an outdoor pool, rooftop plaza, business center, dog park as well as controlled access and 24-hour emergency maintenance.

Information.LongDescription: At Lakeside everything is fresh and new, inside and out. You'll be able to cook in your brand new kitchen with maple cabinets and stainless appliances. Your apartment home will have an oversized balcony or patio, outdoor storage, oversized closets, a washer dryer, and 5 foot windows. Lakeside's amenities surpass all others. When living at Lakeside you have access to resort-style amenities including 3 sparkling pools to choose from, an outdoor hot tub, a fitness center, a Starbucks wireless cafe, a sand volleyball court, a playground area, tennis and sports courts, a dog park, a car wash center and much more. Whether riding your bike around the lakes or enjoying the scenic overlook from your balcony, you are sure to find a way to appreciate Lakeside's distinctive views. The perfect complement to the way you like to live. Just in case you don't have enough to do within Lakeside, convenient shopping, restaurants and movie theaters are just minutes away in Centreville.
